These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, disco, techno
3 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig, chinchilla
1. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
3. the owner of the rat is the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | hip-hop | disco |
| Pet    | guinea-pig    | chinchilla | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, peas, radish
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, scrabble
1. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
2. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person eating radish##1
4. the person playing backgammon is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food       | peas | radish | eggplant |
| Game   | scrabble    | backgammon     | mah-jongg        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, satire, mystery
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, blend, vegafina
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery     | satire | disaster |
| Cigar   | blend | chaman     | vegafina  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, folk, dubstep
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, blend
1. the fan of folk is the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the fan of electronic is the blend-smoker##1
3. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | folk  | electronic  |
| Cigar         | chaman  | oliveros | blend |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, documentary
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, fonseca, oliveros
1. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching animation movies and the swisher-smoker##2
2. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre         | animation   | documentary | comedy    |
| Cigar   | fonseca | oliveros     | swisher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, goat, chinchilla
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, bus, helicopter
1. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Pet   | goat | chinchilla | rabbit   |
| Transport   | helicopter     | tram    | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, ship, van
City: venice, miami, paris
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person traveling to paris and the person driving the van##2
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Transport   | van | jet-ski | ship |
| City           | miami         | venice         | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, family, romance
City: nizza, rome, marseilles
1. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to rome and the person watching scientific movies##2
2. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | romance | scientific |
| City    | rome    | nizza | marseilles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, blend, bluemaster
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, mystery, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster   | blend  | aristoff  |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero | mystery | romance |

