.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese, german
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the german##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | german      | japanese |
| Hobby       | traveling | filmmaking | magic-tricks   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, february, october
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, yellow, lilac
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who likes lilac is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Birthday         | february | october | november |
| Color   | yellow | lilac   | fuchsia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, lettuce, corn
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, azalea, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person eating cranberry is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | corn | lettuce | cranberry |
| Flower     | azalea     | sunflower   | balloon-flower        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
