There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, tea
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of classical##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | soul | indie   |
