.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, daisy
There 3 different types of food: potato, asparagus, lemon
1. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growsiris and the person eating asparagus##2
2. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating asparagus is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Flower   | iris | daisy | orchid |
| Food     | potato    | lemon  | asparagus   |

