2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the writer##3
4. the writer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Job   | librarian  | writer     | manager |
| Transport   | motorbike | subway | car    |

