2. the ranch-style house is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the palace house is in an odd position##4
4. the victorian house is on the left or right of the palace house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Nationality          | colombian | chinese | brazilian  |
| House   | ranch-style      | victorian  | palace |

