.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
3 different games are played: canasta, bridge, monopoly
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, sports, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
3. the person playing monopoly is the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Game         | monopoly | canasta   | bridge |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | animation | fantasy      |

