.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, milk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, june, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage     | almond-milk  | milk   | hot-chocolate |
| Birthday   | september | june | may       |

 